-- Soitec Surges After Confirming Second-Quarter, First-Half Sales Targets
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-27T07:02:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/soitec-surges-after-confirming-second-quarter-first-half-sales-targets.html
Soitec SA shares climbed after the
company confirmed its sales targets for the second quarter and
first half.  The shares jumped 6.2 percent to 7.38 euros at 9:02 a.m. in
Paris.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
